heading.$invariant: What products are in the range?

contentData.heading: Four Channel Receiver
contentData.text: The TrioCode MegaCode Receiver is a powerful solution that can effortlessly operate up to four separate devices. With its user-friendly menu-driven control system and convenient LCD display, managing a large number of remote controls and various operating inputs has never been easier. This advanced receiver empowers you to effortlessly handle up to 511 remotes, granting you unparalleled flexibility and control. Say goodbye to complexity and embrace simplicity with the TrioCode MegaCode Receiver from Automatic Technology.

contentData.heading: Single & Dual Channel Receivers
contentData.text: These receivers seamlessly integrate with other compatible non-Automatic Technology appliances in your home, giving you the convenience of activating them using your Automatic Technology remote control. Expand the capabilities of your access control system and enjoy the simplicity of controlling multiple devices with a single remote. With our stand-alone receivers, you can effortlessly enhance the connectivity and functionality of your automation setup. Experience the convenience and flexibility of activating various appliances thanks to our innovative stand-alone receivers.

contentData.heading: Control Board
contentData.text: Experience ultimate control and flexibility with the CB-6 Logic controller. This advanced controller empowers you to effortlessly manage up to two AC motors, whether they are single or three phase, using microprocessor logic. With a range of input triggers including Safety Beam, swipe card, loop detector, and more, the CB-6 Logic controller offers true versatility. Take advantage of the optional plug-in receiver feature to enable access via a remote transmitter, adding an extra layer of convenience to your automation system. Trust in the CB-6 Logic controller to deliver seamless operation and enhanced functionality for your motorised systems.
